DISCIPLINARY CASES

2009-1535. Cleveland Metro. Bar Assn. v. Kealy.

This cause came on for further consideration upon respondent’s filing of a response to the show cause order issued by this court on June 3, 2010. Upon consideration thereof,

It is ordered that no action shall be taken at this time, provided respondent files his affidavit of compliance within ten days of the date of this order.
